WITH CEL_TMP_ERPOrder AS (
    SELECT 
        *
        , ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "ERPOrder"."InitialUniqueName" ORDER BY "ERPOrder"."VersionNumber" DESC) AS RN
    FROM "ERPOrder"
)
SELECT
    'ERPOrder_' || "ERPOrder"."InitialUniqueName" AS "ID",
    'PurchaseOrder_300' || "ERPOrder"."OrderID" AS "PurchaseOrder",
    "ERPOrder"."InitialUniqueName" AS "InitialUniqueName",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."SubmitDate" AS timestamp)) AS "SubmitDate",
    "ERPOrder"."OrderStatusPunchOutDisabled" AS "OrderStatusPunchOutDisabled",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."ChargeAmount" AS float) AS "ChargeAmount",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."LastModified" AS timestamp)) AS "LastModified",
    "ERPOrder"."OrderConfirmationState" AS "OrderConfirmationState",
    "ERPOrder"."AdvancedShipNoticeState" AS "AdvancedShipNoticeState",
    "ERPOrder"."ChangedBy" AS "ChangedBy",
    "ERPOrder"."OrderConfirmationStatusString" AS "OrderConfirmationStatusString",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."ResubmitDate" AS timestamp)) AS "ResubmitDate",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."NumberCleared" AS int) AS "NumberCleared",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountBilled" AS float) AS "AmountBilled",
    "ERPOrder"."UniqueName" AS "UniqueName",
    "ERPOrder"."ManuallyOrdered" AS "ManuallyOrdered",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountCleared" AS float) AS "AmountCleared",
    "ERPOrder"."OriginatingSystem" AS "OriginatingSystem",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."NumberReceivableLineItems" AS integer) AS "NumberReceivableLineItems",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountReconciled" AS float) AS "AmountReconciled",
    "ERPOrder"."StatusString" AS "StatusString",
    "ERPOrder"."IsBlanketOrder" AS "IsBlanketOrder",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountInvoiced" AS float) AS "AmountInvoiced",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."TimeUpdated" AS timestamp)) AS "TimeUpdated",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."VersionNumber" AS integer) AS "VersionNumber",
    "ERPOrder"."Type" AS "Type",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."ExpirationDate" AS timestamp)) AS "ExpirationDate",
    "ERPOrder"."IsServiceOrder" AS "IsServiceOrder",
    "ERPOrder"."Requisition" AS "Requisition",
    "ERPOrder"."ApprovedState" AS "ApprovedState",
    "ERPOrder"."InvoicedState" AS "InvoicedState",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."HoldTillDate" AS timestamp)) AS "HoldTillDate",
    "ERPOrder"."ReceivedState" AS "ReceivedState",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."NumberReceivableOrders" AS integer) AS "NumberReceivableOrders",
    "ERPOrder"."OrderID" AS "OrderID",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."CreateDate" AS timestamp)) AS "CreateDate",
    "ERPOrder"."Conditions" AS "Conditions",
    "ERPOrder"."Name" AS "Name",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."TimeCreated" AS timestamp)) AS "TimeCreated",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."Version" AS integer) AS "Version",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."InvoicedDate" AS timestamp)) AS "InvoicedDate",
    "ERPOrder"."UsePOLineNumberForIntegration" AS "UsePOLineNumberForIntegration",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."ApprovedDate" AS timestamp)) AS "ApprovedDate",
    "ERPOrder"."OrderedState" AS "OrderedState",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."PreviousApprovalRequestsVersion" AS integer) AS "PreviousApprovalRequestsVersion",
    "ERPOrder"."OrderMethodCategory" AS "OrderMethodCategory",
    "ERPOrder"."RejectionReason" AS "RejectionReason",
    "ERPOrder"."Active" AS "Active",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."ReceivedDate" AS timestamp)) AS "ReceivedDate",

    "ERPOrder"."OriginatingSystemReferenceID" AS "OriginatingSystemReferenceID",
    "ERPOrder"."Closed" AS "Closed",
    "ERPOrder"."SupplierLocation_State" AS "SupplierLocationState",
    "ERPOrder"."SupplierLocation_Phone" AS "SupplierLocationPhone",
    "ERPOrder"."SupplierLocation_Country_UniqueName" AS "SupplierLocationCountryUniqueName",
    "ERPOrder"."SupplierLocation_PostalCode" AS "SupplierLocationPostalCode",
    "ERPOrder"."SupplierLocation_City" AS "SupplierLocationCity",

    "ERPOrder"."Conditions_UniqueName" AS "ConditionsUniqueName",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."Conditions_TAndCVersion" AS float) AS "ConditionsTAndCVersion",

    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."TotalCost_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" AS float) AS "TotalCostApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."TotalCost_Amount" AS float) AS "TotalCostAmount",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."TotalCost_ConversionDate" AS timestamp)) AS "TotalCostConversionDate",
    "ERPOrder"."TotalCost_Currency_UniqueName" AS "TotalCostCurrencyUniqueName",
    "ERPOrder"."Requester_UniqueName" AS "RequesterUniqueName",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountAccepted_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountAcceptedAmountInReportingCurrency",

    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountAccepted_Amount" AS float) AS "AmountAcceptedAmount",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountAccepted_ConversionDate" AS timestamp)) AS "AmountAcceptedConversionDate",
    "ERPOrder"."AmountAccepted_Currency_UniqueName" AS "AmountAcceptedCurrencyUniqueName",
    "ERPOrder"."ChangedBy_UniqueName" AS "ChangedByUniqueName",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountBilled_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountBilledAmountInReportingCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountBilled_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountBilledApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountBilled_Amount" AS float) AS "AmountBilledAmount",

    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountCleared_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountClearedAmountInReportingCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountCleared_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountClearedApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountCleared_Amount" AS float) AS "AmountClearedAmount",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>, TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountCleared_ConversionDate" AS timestamp)) AS "AmountClearedConversionDate",

    "ERPOrder"."PaymentTerms_UniqueName" AS "PaymentTermsUniqueName",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountReconciled_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountReconciledAmountInReportingCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountReconciled_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountReconciledApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountReconciled_Amount" AS float) AS "AmountReconciledAmount",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountReconciled_ConversionDate" AS timestamp)) AS "AmountReconciledConversionDate",
    "ERPOrder"."AmountReconciled_Currency_UniqueName" AS "AmountReconciledCurrencyUniqueName",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountRejected_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountRejectedAmountInReportingCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountRejected_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountRejectedApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountRejected_Amount" AS float) AS "AmountRejectedAmount",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountRejected_ConversionDate" AS timestamp)) AS "AmountRejectedConversionDate",
    "ERPOrder"."AmountRejected_Currency_UniqueName" AS "AmountRejectedCurrencyUniqueName",
    "ERPOrder"."Supplier_UniqueName" AS "SupplierUniqueName",
    "ERPOrder"."Supplier_Name" AS "SupplierName",
    "ERPOrder"."PreviousVersion_UniqueName" AS "PreviousVersionUniqueName",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountInvoiced_AmountInReportingCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountInvoicedAmountInReportingCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountInvoiced_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" AS float) AS "AmountInvoicedApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
    TRY_CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountInvoiced_Amount" AS float) AS "AmountInvoicedAmount",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("ERPOrder"."AmountInvoiced_ConversionDate" AS timestamp)) AS "AmountInvoicedConversionDate",
    "ERPOrder"."AmountInvoiced_Currency_UniqueName" AS "AmountInvoicedCurrencyUniqueName",
    "ERPOrder"."Preparer_UniqueName" AS "PreparerUniqueName",
    "ERPOrder"."Requisition_UniqueName" AS "RequisitionUniqueName",
    "ERPOrder"."CompanyCode_UniqueName" AS "CompanyCodeUniqueName"
FROM "CEL_TMP_ERPOrder" AS "ERPOrder"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "ERPOrder"."RN" = 1
    AND  "ERPOrder"."Active" = 'true'
